27 workers trapped in California tunnel rescued overnight
To stream News 8 on your phone, you need the News 8 app.
Download the News 8 app
Twenty-seven workers were on the site of a wastewater project when the tunnel collapsed. Within hours, hundreds of first responders brought everyone to the surface.
